 * 01-Nov-2000: Allocation checks
 * 10-May-1997: Jamie Zawinski <jwz@@jwz.org> compatible with xscreensaver
 * 01-Dec-1995: Patched for VMS <joukj@@hrem.stm.tudelft.nl>
